Yars Client (Yet Another RESTAS Server Client)

Lightweight alternative to RESTAS that uses the Clustericious framework.


Install the package:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



Create a config file (~/etc/Yars.conf) that looks something like this:

---
url : http://localhost:10001
port : 10001
host : localhost
ssh_tunnel :
  remote_host : omidev.gsfc.nasa.gov
  server_host : devarch11
  server_port : '8300'



